\id 1JN 1YW - Bible Iyansi 
\h 1 YWAN 
\toc1 Un'kaan atàtwɛb wà Ywan 
\toc2 1 YWAN 
\toc3 1Yw 
\mt2 Un'kaan atàtwɛb wà 
\mt1 Ywan 
\imt1 Nsɛmà 
\ip Un'kaan atàtwɛb wà Ywan bàtöm anki itàkal akà ikööŋ mpɛl, itàkal akà mbuur afàler ikööŋ. Wa afàbiil kà indübà ntɔn muyöb naa ukwen a un'tɔŋ bà aben, anà musà kà igyɛɛŋ aklistɔ bamwɛy abà ban'tɔn muman naa Yɛsu wà asànaa: « Klistɔ » awà kàsɔ̈ɔ̈l Nzam. 
\is1 Un'dim a ndaa 
\ip Nsɛmà yà ntsà. An'kyän ande manswà mà unsà « ndaa ifàpà mɔ̈ɔ̈ ». Nde wàmusà kam naa un'bään a un'tüüb anà Nzam wà udu a mwan ande Yɛsu Klistɔ anà udu a imbäl a an'tööm. Un'kaan awà we abyà itiir byeel byàkölàköl. 
\ip Itiir kyà tàtwɛb kyà naa: Nzam wà pɛɛlà. Mukal unsà pɛɛlà, un'kaan awà wàmulɔm naa bàsyäl nswɛɛŋ a ukwen. 
\ip Itiir kyàyweel kyà ntɔn ukwen amwɛy anà bumwɛy. 
\ip Un'kaan awà akwen muswaŋ làkwikilà aŋàböŋ. Wa alɔɔmà ngyamàkà ntɔn baar bàfàler isal ibe anà muyɔɔb naa Mwan a Nzam mpɛl afàsyen u ngyööb a ndandaa naa Nzam wà nà. 
\ip Ndaa atàtwɛb ikyäänà làsaŋ aŋàbwaŋ là nà, wɛɛ apà yà ntɔn: « Ndaa ayà ifàpà mɔ̈ɔ̈ » u mbwo a ngyööb aŋàsöön. Ya yà ndaa akün yun'tüüb anà Nzam, anà Mwan ande, anà aŋangɔɔm, anà atɔŋ. 
\ip Unsà an'kyän a wa ŋakwo, un'kaan a Ywan wàtàtwɛb wàmufitaŋà làsaŋ aŋàbwaŋ là Ywan. Ukwen a mbääb bàsyefurà uboo a un'kaan wàyweel anà wàtär, amyà myàfü akà mbuur bàfàbel naa « un'dweer ». Abun, nkye in'kaan ami myà un'söön umwɛy wa? Yà mpay mukyey. 
\ie  
\c 1  
\s1 Ndaa a mɔ̈ɔ̈ 
\p  
\v 1 Ndaa ifàpà mɔ̈ɔ̈ yàkäl fà nsɛmà. Bi kàwem ya. Bi kàmɛn ya u mii abi ŋakwo. Bi kàsyeebà ya, anà an'kɔɔ abi màbä ya.  
\v 2 Ntɔn mɔ̈ɔ̈ kàkyer ayàmɛnà, anà bi kàkyer un'man, bi kun'tɛɛl imbäl anà bi kàlakyään mɔ̈ɔ̈ a mbul a in'tye awà kàkäl apà Taa anà kàyàmɛnà ntɔn bi.  
\v 3 Ndaa kàmɛn bi anà kàwem bi, bi ikyäänà ya akà bɛ sye, ntɔn bɛ sye làkäl unsà un'tüüb anà bi. Kyekà, un'tüüb abi wà un'tüüb ibà bi awà anà Taa anà Mwan ande Yɛsu Klistɔ.  
\v 4 Isàkal naa bi kàlasöönà indiir abi, yà ntɔn un'sak abi ukäl wàŋàkwo. 
\s1 Nzam wà pɛɛlà 
\p  
\v 5 Le làsaŋ kàwem bi akà Yɛsu Klistɔ anà ikàlakyäänà bi: Nzam wà pɛɛlà, anà amu nde làpib latɛy. 
\p  
\v 6 Isàkal naa bi iswaŋà ngaal naa bi ibà un'tüüb anà nde, wɛɛ mɔ̈ɔ̈ abi wà unsà làpib, bi ibà baar a loor, bi ifàsyääl anki ndandaa.  
\v 7 Isàkal naa mɔ̈ɔ̈ abi wà uboo a pɛɛlà, asànaa nde ŋakwo wà uboo a pɛɛlà, bi ibà uboo un'tüüb bi a bi, anà an'kil a Yɛsu, Mwan ande, màfàpöŋ man'be abi manswà.  
\v 8 Isàkal naa bi iswaŋà ngaal naa bi man'be matɛy, bi ban'bwiy bi ŋàkwo ndwaŋ, anà ndandaa yatɛy amu bi.  
\v 9 Wɛɛ, isàkal naa bi ban'kyey man'be abi, Nzam wà lää anà balàbal: nde asidwääl man'be abi anà asipööŋ unsà indiir byanswà mpa abyà balàbal.  
\v 10 Isàkal naa bi ikyeyà uyɔl naa bi man'be kàkyer anki, bi bun'buulà mbuur a loor, anà ndaa ande yatɛy amu bi. 
\c 2  
\s1 Mbaay a Yɛsu 
\p  
\v 1 Baan amɛ, amàlasöön mɛ indiir bi yà ntɔn bɛ làkɔ̈ɔ̈n akyer man'be. Wɛɛ isàkal naa mbuur kan'kyer man'be, bi ibye anà nkalsà tsütsü apà Taa, Yɛsu Klistɔ, awà balàbal.  
\v 2 Ntɔn nde wà mbuur kàkyey mukal ibɔɔn ntɔn man'be abi, kà ntɔn bi mpɛl anki, wɛɛ sye ntɔn baar a mɛɛn manswà. 
\s1 Nswɛɛŋ a ukwen 
\p  
\v 3 Bi ibye anà an'kyän a ndandaa naa bi iyöb Klistɔ, isàkal naa bi ifàkyey nswɛɛŋ ande.  
\v 4 Isàkal naa mbuur an'tɛn naa: « Mɛ in'kyun'yöb », wɛɛ nde ufàkyey anki nswɛɛŋ ande, nde wà mbuur a loor, ndandaa amu nde yatɛy.  
\v 5 Wɛɛ, mbuur akyeyà ndaa ande, amu nde, ukwen a Nzam a ndandaa bàŋàyɔl, apan, bi ban'kyey naa bi ibà amu nde.  
\v 6 Mbuur awà ukyeyà uyɔl naa nde wà amu Klistɔ, wɛy nde ŋakwo uläb mbwo kàkyenà nde. 
\p  
\v 7 Ankwen amɛ, mɛ kà nswɛɛŋ akün anki amàlasöön, wɛɛ nswɛɛŋ itaan ayà làwɛl bɛ fà nsɛmà. Nswɛɛŋ yà itaan ayi, yà ndaa ayà làwem bɛ.  
\v 8 Wɛɛ yà nswɛɛŋ akün mɛ alàsɔ̈ɔ̈n, ya yà ndandaa amu nde anà amu bɛ, ntɔn mpib yan'lyaaŋ, taaŋ lan'yaanà. 
\p  
\v 9 Mbuur awà ukyeyà uyɔl mukal uboo a pɛɛlà, wɛɛ nde ayiiŋà un'tɔŋ ande, tii kunà nde wà uboo a mpib.  
\v 10 Mbuur awà akwen un'tɔŋ ande, nde wà uboo a pɛɛlà, akà undiir mwɛy tɛy amu nde kan'kwo mukun'bwiy.  
\v 11 Wɛɛ, mbuur awà uyiiŋà un'tɔŋ ande wà uboo a mpib anà nde uyöb anki naa nde akyà ken, ntɔn mpib yan'dübà mii ande. 
\q1  
\v 12 Baan amɛ, mɛ amàlasöön naa: bàmàladwääl nkul ntɔn ikɔb a Yɛsu Klistɔ. 
\q1  
\v 13 Ataa, mɛ amàlasɔ̈ɔ̈n, ntɔn bɛ làkyàyöb mbuur awà fà nsɛmà. 
\q1 Baan atö, mɛ amàlasöön, ntɔn bɛ làwɛl iböŋ kusà a Un'be. 
\p  
\v 14 Baan amɛ, mɛ kàkyer alasöön, ntɔn bɛ làkyun'yöb Taa. 
\q1 Ataa, mɛ kàkyer alasöön, ntɔn bɛ làkyun'yöb mbuur awà fà nsɛmà. 
\q1 Atö, mɛ kàkyer alasöön, ntɔn bɛ làbà ngwal: ndaa a Nzam ifàbwaay uboo a bɛ anà bɛ làkyàwal iböŋ kusà a Un'be. 
\p  
\v 15 Abun, bɛ twon lan'kwen mɛɛn, itàkal indiir abyà uboo a mɛɛn. Isàkal naa mbuur akwen mɛɛn, ukwen a Taa amu nde batɛy.  
\v 16 Ntɔn undiir wanswà awà uboo a mɛɛn: ilään a ndür, ukwen a mii, uyɔl unsà indiir mpa byàfàfà akà Taa, wɛɛ ifàfà u mɛɛn.  
\v 17 Kyekà, mɛɛn màmulyaaŋ anà indiir abyà uboo. Wɛɛ mbuur afàkyer ukwen a Nzam afàkal mbul a in'tye. 
\s1 Un'yiiŋ a Klistɔ 
\p  
\v 18 Baan amɛ, lalà là taaŋ a ntsüü. Bɛ làkyer awem, bàkyäänà naa un'yiiŋ mwɛy wà Klistɔ akyer ayà, kyekà sɛmà apanà ayiiŋ a Klistɔ bàpaa mbɔɔn. Apan bi ban'yöb naa lalà là taaŋ a ntsüü.  
\v 19 Baar abà bàtoo akà bi, wɛɛ ba bàkäl anki bàbi. Yàlàkal naa ba bàkäl bàbi, ba bàlàbwaay anà bi. Wɛɛ ba bàkyer alwomà amu bi ntɔn ya imɛnà ndandaa naa ba kà bàbi anki. 
\p  
\v 20 Wɛɛ akà bɛ, bɛ bàlasi an'kɔɔ akà aŋin'kyɛɛl, anà bɛ banswà làkyàyöb ya.  
\v 21 Isàkal naa mɛ amàlasöön, kà ntɔn mutɛn anki naa bɛ ndandaa làyöb anki, wɛɛ ntɔn bɛ làkyàyöb naa akà loor làmwɛy làfàfà anki u ndandaa. 
\p  
\v 22 Apan, nà awà mbuur a loor, nkye wà mbuur awà utɔnà naa Yɛsu wà Klistɔ? Ler, un'yiiŋ a Klistɔ, nde mbuur afàtɔn mukyey Taa anà Mwan.  
\v 23 Mbuur wanswà afàtɔn Mwan, Taa sye watɛy amu nde. Mbuur afàkyey Mwan, ayöb Taa sye.  
\v 24 Kyakin, wɛy ndaa làwem bɛ fà nsɛmà ibwaay amu bɛ. Isàkal naa ndaa làwem bɛ fà nsɛmà yan'bwaay amu bɛ, bɛ làsàkal amu Mwan anà amu Taa.  
\v 25 Le ilää kàsi nde ŋakwo: mɔ̈ɔ̈ a mbul a in'tye. 
\p  
\v 26 Indiir abi mɛ kàlasöön ntɔn baar bàfàleŋ mukàlabwiy ndwaŋ.  
\v 27 Wɛɛ akà bɛ, Dweelà awà làwɛl bɛ akà Klistɔ, kan'bwaay amu bɛ. Abun, ndöŋ yatɛy naa mbuur ufàlalɔŋ. Ntɔn Dweelà ande wàmukàlalɔɔŋà indiir byanswà: nde wà ndandaa, nde loor ufàtà anki, nde kàlalɔŋ naa bɛ lan'bwaay amu nde. 
\p  
\v 28 Abun, baan amɛ, làbwaay amu nde, ntɔn taaŋ uyamɛnà nde, bi iyàkal bàŋàtsim, ntɔn mukɔɔn asàkal aŋàyɔl a nswɛn kusà a nde.  
\v 29 Ntɔn bɛ làkyàyöb naa nde wà balàbal, làyöb naa mbuur wanswà afàsyääl balàbal, bàmubɔr amu nde. 
\c 3  
\s1 Baan a Nzam 
\p  
\v 1 Taaràbi kikwen mbɔɔn, lalan kipɛ nde kab: bi bibeelà baan a Nzam, ndandaa bi ibà abwɛy! Kyakin, mɛɛn miyöb anki, ntɔn ma màyöb anki Nzam.  
\v 2 Ankwen amɛ, sɛmà apanà bi ibà baan a Nzam, wɛɛ ayà isàkal bi ŋàtàmɛnà anki. Bi ikyàyöb naa umpal usàmɛnà nde, bi isàkal asànaa nde, ntɔn bi isuman asànaa awà nde.  
\v 3 Mbuur wanswà an'sà làkyän amu nde, wàmupööŋ nde ŋakwo asànaa Yɛsu Klistɔ ŋakwo wàŋàpɔŋà. 
\p  
\v 4 Mbuur awà an'kyer man'be, an'kyer sye ube, ntɔn man'be mà ube.  
\v 5 Wɛɛ bɛ làkyàyöb naa nde kàyàmɛnà ntɔn mulwom man'be, amu nde man'be matɛy.  
\v 6 Mbuur wanswà awà amu nde ufàkyer anki man'be. Mbuur wanswà afàkyer man'be, wàmuswaŋ naa nde kun'mɛn anki anà kun'yöb anki. 
\p  
\v 7 Baan amɛ, mbuur twon kàlabwiy ndwaŋ! Mbuur awà afàkyer ndaa a balàbal, wà balàbal, asànaa Klistɔ ŋakwo wà balàbal.  
\v 8 Mbuur afàkyer man'be wà mbuur a ileŋ, ntɔn ileŋ afàkyer man'be fà nsɛmà. Mwan a Nzam kàyàmɛnà ntɔn mudwa isal a ileŋ. 
\p  
\v 9 Mbuur awà bàbör amu Nzam, ufàfàkyer anki man'be, ntɔn mbɛŋ ande yan'bwaay amu nde, nde ufàkwo anki mukyer man'be, ntɔn Nzam wà Taarànde.  
\v 10 Le undiir afàpà nsöön ubwaŋàbwaŋ uboo a baan a Nzam anà baan a ileŋ: mbuur wanswà mpa afàkyer balàbal, itàkal mpa afàkwen un'tɔŋ ande, kà wà mwan a Nzam anki. 
\p  
\v 11 Ntɔn alà làsaŋ làwem bɛ fà nsɛmà: wɛy bi ikwen bi a bi.  
\v 12 Wɛy bi ikɔ̈ɔ̈n akyer asànaa Kayin awà kàkäl mbuur a Un'be, waa kàdwä utɔŋ ande. Ntɔn nkye kun'dwä nde? Ntɔn isal ande byàkäl byà ibe, wɛɛ byà un'tɔŋ ande byàkäl byà balàbal.  
\v 13 Atɔŋ, twon lan'man ndaa yà ubem, isàkal naa mɛɛn màmàlayiiŋ.  
\v 14 Bi, bi ikyàyöb naa bi bàfü kà ukwà tii uboo a mɔ̈ɔ̈, ntɔn bi ifàkwen atɔŋ. Mbuur mpa awà anà ukwen, wà uboo a ukwà.  
\v 15 Ntɔn mbuur awà un'yiiŋ a un'tɔŋ ande wà un'dwää. Anà bɛ làkyàyöb naa akà un'dwää mwɛy awe anà mɔ̈ɔ̈ a mbul a in'tye amu nde watɛy.  
\v 16 Le, apanà bi ban'yöb ukwen: Yɛsu Klistɔ kàpɛ mɔ̈ɔ̈ ande ntɔn bi. Bi sye ikyer asànaa nde, bi ipà mɔ̈ɔ̈ abi ntɔn atɔŋ.  
\v 17 Isàkal naa mbuur u mɛɛn mà we anà indiir mbɔɔn, nde umɛn un'tɔŋ ande u mpay, wɛɛ nde kun'kääŋ mpem, ukwen a Nzam ban'kwo mukal aben amu nde?  
\v 18 Baan amɛ, wɛy bi ikɔ̈ɔ̈n akwen nà u ndaa anà làlem mpɛl, wɛɛ unsà isal anà u ndandaa. 
\s1 Làkyän kusà a Nzam 
\p  
\v 19 Abun, bi waa isàyöb naa bi ibà baar a ndandaa, anà mpem abi waa isàkal yà duu kusà a Nzam.  
\v 20 Ntɔn, itàkal naa mpem abi yàmukifüünà, bi ikyàyöb naa Nzam kan'söön mpem abi anà nde akyàyöb indiir byanswà.  
\v 21 Atɔŋ amɛ bànkwen, isàkal naa mpem abi ikifüünà anki, bi ibye anà làkyän kusà a Nzam.  
\v 22 Abun, bi isàwal undiir wanswà isàlɔm bi akà nde, ntɔn bi ban'kyey nswɛɛŋ ande anà bi ifàkyer ukwen ande.  
\v 23 Le nswɛɛŋ ande: bi musà làkwikilà kà ikɔb a Mwan ande Yɛsu Klistɔ anà bi ikwen bi a bi, asànaa kiswɛŋ nde.  
\v 24 Mbuur afàsyäl nswɛɛŋ ande wà wà Nzam, anà Nzam wà amu nde. Apan, bi ban'yöb naa nde wà uboo a bi, u mbwo a Dweelà kipɛ nde. 
\c 4  
\s1 Dweelà a Nzam anà libör 
\p  
\v 1 Ankwen amɛ, twon làn'sà làkwikilà akà baar bàkakyeyà uyɔl naa ba bye anà Dweelà, wɛɛ lasii, ntɔn muyöb naa nkye an'dweelà amà akà ba man'fà akà Nzam, ntɔn aŋangɔɔm a loor mbɔɔn bàkyàpää u mɛɛn.  
\v 2 Apan bɛ lan'yöb Dweelà a Nzam: dweelà lanswà lan'kyey naa Yɛsu Klistɔ kàyi u ndür, nde wà wà Nzam.  
\v 3 Wɛɛ mbuur wanswà afàtɔn mukyey Yɛsu, akà nde Dweelà a Nzam watɛy, wɛɛ dweelà a un'yiiŋ a Klistɔ: bɛ làkyàwem naa nde awà akyer asàyà, anà apanà, nde kàkyàyà itaan u mɛɛn.  
\v 4 Wɛɛ bɛ, baan amɛ, bɛ baan a Nzam, bɛ làkyàwal iböŋ kusà a aŋangɔɔm aban, ntɔn Dweelà awafàsal uboo a bɛ wà wàngwal aŋàsöön dweelà làfàyaal mɛɛn.  
\v 5 Ba bà baar a mɛɛn. Ba sye bàfàtɛn ndaa a mɛɛn, mɛɛn waa màfàwem.  
\v 6 Wɛɛ bi, bi ibà baan a Nzam. Mbuur awà ayöb Nzam, wàmukiweemà. Mbuur mpa awà wà Nzam, kiweemà anki. Apan, bi ban'yöb Dweelà a ndandaa anà dweelà làfàbwiy ndwaŋ. 
\s1 Nzam wà ukwen 
\p  
\v 7 Abun, atɔŋ amɛ, wɛy bi ikwen bi a bi. Ntɔn ukwen bàfàfà akà Nzam, anà mbuur wanswà afàkwen, bun'bör amu Nzam anà nde akyun'kwen.  
\v 8 Wɛɛ, mbuur mpa afàkwen kàyöb anki Nzam, ntɔn Nzam wà ukwen.  
\v 9 Apan, làler, ukwen a Nzam bàfàmɛnà aben uboo a bi: Nzam kàtöm Mwan ande mwɛy mpɛl u mɛɛn, ntɔn bi iwɛl mɔ̈ɔ̈ u mbwo a nde.  
\v 10 Le, ukwen ininà: kà bi anki kàkwen Nzam, wɛɛ nde kikwen, waa kàtöm Mwan ande asànaa ibɔɔn ntɔn ndwääl a man'be abi.  
\v 11 Ankwen amɛ, isàkal naa Nzam kikwen abun, bi sye, ikwen bi a bi.  
\v 12 Akà mbuur mwɛy kàtääŋ anki Nzam. Isàkal naa bi ban'kwen bi a bi, Nzam wà amu bi, anà ukwen ande amu bi bàŋàkwo.  
\v 13 Unsà yayi, bi ifàtà imbäl naa bi ibà amu nde, anà nde amu bi: nde kipɛ Dweelà ande.  
\v 14 Anà bi, bi kàkyer un'tääŋ, waa bi ifàtà imbäl naa Taa kàtöm Mwan asànaa Un'tswää a mɔ̈ɔ̈ a mɛɛn.  
\v 15 Mbuur wanswà afàtà imbäl naa Yɛsu wà Mwan a Nzam, Nzam wà amu nde, nde wà amu Nzam.  
\v 16 Waa bi, bi ban'yöb anà ban'sà làkwikilà naa Nzam akyikwen. 
\p Nzam wà ukwen. Mbuur awà uboo a ukwen wà amu Nzam, anà Nzam wà amu nde.  
\v 17 Undiir uleŋà ukwen aŋàkwo uboo abi, wà naa bi ikäl aŋàyɔl a làkyän kà ilä a nsaŋ. Bi isàkal abwɛy, ntɔn mɔ̈ɔ̈ abi u mɛɛn mà wà asànaa awà wànde.  
\v 18 Bɔɔmà batɛy uboo a ukwen. Ukwen aŋàkwo bàfàpiy bɔɔmà, ntɔn bɔɔmà bafàyà mpal bàfàdil ntaaŋàmbar. Anà mbur afàman bɔɔmà ukwen ande kà bàŋakwo anki. 
\p  
\v 19 Akà bi, bi ikyer afàkwen, ntɔn Nzam kàtwab atikwen.  
\v 20 Isàkal naa mbuur an'tɛn naa: « Mɛ in'kwen Nzam », wɛɛ nde an'yiiŋà un'tɔŋ ande, nde wà mbuur a loor, ntɔn mbuur mpa ukwen un'tɔŋ awà ukàmanà nde, ukwe anki mukwen Nzam mpa ukàmanà nde.  
\v 21 Anà, le nswɛɛŋ ban'kwo bi mukaar akà nde: mbuur awà akwen Nzam, wɛy ukwen sye un'tɔŋ ande. 
\c 5  
\s1 Iböŋ u mɛɛn 
\p  
\v 1 Mbuur awà an'sà làkwikilà naa Yɛsu wà Klistɔ, bàmubɔr amu Nzam, anà mbuur awà akwen Taa, mbuur afàpà mɔ̈ɔ̈, nde afàkwen sye mbuur bàbɔ̈r amu Nzam.  
\v 2 Muyöb naa bi ikwen baan a Nzam, bi ikwen Nzam anà isyääl nswɛɛŋ ande.  
\v 3 Ntɔn mukwen Nzam yà mukwey nswɛɛŋ ande. Nswɛɛŋ ande ayi buur batɛy,  
\v 4 ntɔn mbuur wanswà bàbör amu Nzam, wà ŋiböŋ u mɛɛn. Anà mbwo muwal iböŋ u mɛɛn yà làkwikilà abi.  
\v 5 Nà awà ŋiböŋ u mɛɛn, isàkɔɔn akal mbuur afàsà làkwikilà naa Yɛsu wà Mwan a Nzam? 
\s1 Imbäl ntɔn Yɛsu Klistɔ 
\p  
\v 6 Yɛsu Klistɔ wà mbuur kàyi u mbwo a an'dà anà an'kil, kà nà unsà an'dà mpɛl anki, wɛɛ unsà an'dà anà an'kil, anà Dweelà ataa imbäl, ntɔn Dweelà wàndandaa.  
\v 7 Abun, ba batär bàmutà imbäl,  
\v 8 dweelà, an'dà anà an'kil, bya byàtär byà mwɛy.  
\v 9 Isàkal naa bi ban'kyey imbäl a baar, imbäl a Nzam kyà kyàkölàköl, ntɔn kya kyà imbäl a Nzam, nde imbäl aki kàtɛ ntɔn Mwan ande.  
\v 10 Mbuur awe anà làkwikilà akà Mwan a Nzam, nde we anà imbäl aki amu nde ŋakwo. Wɛɛ mbuur akɔ̈ɔ̈n làkwikilà, Nzam afun'buul mbuur a loor, ntɔn nde làkwikilà latɛy unsà imbäl kàtɛ Nzam ntɔn Mwan ande.  
\v 11 Le imbäl ki: Nzam kipɛ mɔ̈ɔ̈ a mbul a in'tye, wɛɛ mɔ̈ɔ̈ wà amu Mwan ande.  
\v 12 Mbuur awe anà Mwan we anà mɔ̈ɔ̈, mbuur awà akɔ̈ɔ̈n Mwan a Nzam, nde mɔ̈ɔ̈ watɛy. 
\s1 Mɔ̈ɔ̈ a mbul a in'tye 
\p  
\v 13 Amàlasöön mɛ indiir abi yà ntɔn naa bɛ làyöb naa bɛ labye anà mɔ̈ɔ̈ a mbul a in'tye, bɛ baar làbye anà làkwikilà kà ikɔb a Mwan a Nzam.  
\v 14 Apan, làkyän ibà bi alà kusà a nde lalà: isàkal naa bi ban'lɔm undiir asànaa abà ukwen ande, nde akyer afiwem.  
\v 15 Anà, isàkal naa bi ikyàyöb naa nde akyer afiwem, bi ibye anà làkyän naa bi ban'wal undiir kan'lɔm bi akà nde.  
\v 16 Isàkal naa mbuur an'man un'tɔŋ ande wàmukyer man'be, man'be mpa ifàtwaal ukwà, wɛy nde uyamà, waa Nzam usun'pà mɔ̈ɔ̈, isàkal naa ndandaa man'be kan'kyer nde mun'syen anki kà ukwà. Wɛɛ mye anà man'be màfàsyen mbuur kà ukwà, kà ntɔn man'be a tub amà anki mɛ in'tɛɛnà muyamà.  
\v 17 Ube banswà bà man'be, wɛɛ man'be manswà ifàsyen anki kà ukwà.  
\v 18 Bi ikyàyöb naa mbuur wanswà awà bàbɔ̈r amu Nzam ufàfàkyer anki man'be, ntɔn Mwan a Nzam nde ŋakwo akyer afun'tii. Wɛɛ Un'be kun'kyer anki akà undiir mwɛy.  
\v 19 Bi ikyàyöb naa bi ibà baan a Nzam, wɛɛ mɛɛn manswà mà ungyɛl a imwol a Un'be.  
\v 20 Bi ikyàyöb naa Mwan a Nzam kàkyàyà anà kipɛ un'yɛnà ntɔn muyöb Nzam a ndandaa. Abun, bi ibà uboo a Ndandaa, amu Mwan ande Yɛsu Klistɔ, Nde wà Ndandaa, nde wà Nzam anà mɔ̈ɔ̈ a mbul a in'tye.  
\v 21 Baan amɛ, làkäl bɛ ŋakwo ukwɛl anà itɛk.